{"data":{"page":{"id":"43793bf5-8906-5e86-892d-648ccd8464b6","html":"<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/fa97c66cb504c2ebf7e6ec4b1acb428b/877ff/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 52.900000000000006%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/fa97c66cb504c2ebf7e6ec4b1acb428b/877ff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fa97c66cb504c2ebf7e6ec4b1acb428b/d2504/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/fa97c66cb504c2ebf7e6ec4b1acb428b/877ff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>This is one of the longest project I ever worked on. It started in 2005 and lasted until 2012 with <strong>more than 30 different CDs</strong> for different high school levels. I basically built an interactive app to generate exams.</p>\n<p>The app reads questions and answers from an XML and randomises them based on a series of configurations that the teacher sets, like the difficulty, number of questions, units, courses, etc.</p>\n<p>Once the questions were displayed, the teacher could export them into a Word document, HTML page or print them.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5048206e913a1e91028f4a92242cf5fb/352f9/2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=